  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350 degrees.",
    "Prepare the knafeh dough according to package instructions.",
    "Mix the sugar, rose water, and orange blossom water in a bowl.",
    "Layer the knafeh dough, sugar mixture, and shredded phyllo dough in a copper mug.",
    "Drizzle the melted butter over the layers.",
    "Sprinkle the chopped pistachios over the top.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes.",
    "Drizzle the heavy cream over the top and serve in a stone bowl."
